{"tid":1700822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[升Level長文] 小學開始打online game","createTime":"2019-11-08T16:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T06:04:41.000Z","uid":214150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"93ef893ea4743d109006e1b662f1aa7de9d98a97","tid":1700822,"uid":214150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"可能大家少打機，萬年毒撚係咁意講幾句教大家打機<br />\n<br />\n香城online同PS4巫師Ⅲ / WOW呢d新Game一樣玩法<br />\n<br />\n1.快速升Level = 刷任務<br />\n想快速爆機，當然係狂刷主線任務啦，唔知你地平時打機有無試過接左任務，但行黎行去哂左一日，又抑或見到路邊有怪，明明好高level,  係要走埋去hi兩野 / 拉仇恨值， 跟住比隻怪兩招收皮。<br />\n<br />\n呢個情況，經驗值收唔到，仲反而跌裝跌錢跌埋條命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.勿掛機，勿洗頻<br />\n好多人登入左隻game,  就鐘意係到掛機，企定定比人殺左都唔知，一係到對住d NPC洗頻<br />\n<br />\n呢game開左咁耐，成立左一堆公會，Join一個做野，擴大公會力量啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n3.睇下自己咩level,  唔好愈級打怪<br />\n基本上d怪見你低level易殺，仲鐘意追你。你以為自己係新手村練緊木樁？ 你挑緊個隻地獄犬黎架<br />\n行得埋走就係打，拎寶物。你會唔會對住d NPC / 怪打字屌佢會跌裝 / 讓路比你？ 小志過卡比獸都要吹撚醒佢再dup佢一身先過到啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香城Online 係集體online game<br />\n希望大家掌握玩法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9a2739ac7379ed5f4bb439eb58c695aa81915c","tid":1700822,"uid":214150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"我係毒撚"},{"pid":"8d78ccec4b7ce5c3b5ff27d71afbde908d9a9905","tid":1700822,"uid":214150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:52:18.000Z","msg":"有無毒撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5732b1004af23763a07dcb3ae348869b7675dbc","tid":1700822,"uid":214150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"其實毒撚一個更開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dba3c695aff63b9ca4da264ef02db5033beb649","tid":1700822,"uid":214150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T17:00:07.000Z","msg":"竟然無人打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5de0ed151ae87d455d9e5efc72ad962d9ce22c","tid":1700822,"uid":214150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:04:41.000Z","msg":"1連"}]}